text: LA-41 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by Abdul Majid Khan of Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf. It covers the area of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa in Pakistan. Only refugees from Kashmir Valley settled in Pakistan are eligible to vote. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
